{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Footsy is a chaotic multiplayer soccer party game set inside grandma's house! Smash furniture, shatter bottles, and tumble TVs as you compete in wild, goal-scoring action. Perfect for parties! </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H1.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kick, smash, and outscore your friends in crazy 1v1 soccer matches set in grandma\u2019s house!\u00a0<br>whether it's on the couch or via remote play, friendships will be tested!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_1.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H2.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Smash tables, shatter vases, and tumble TVs in every match. With physics-driven chaos, every kick has the potential to change the game and the house!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_6.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H3.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You only need one stick and one button to start scoring. Anyone can play instantly, but those seeking mastery can perfect their timing, aim, and advanced trick shots to dominate the field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_5.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H4.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you want to play with furniture or without, with a soccer ball, a hockey puck or a mystical changing puzzle cube. You can fully customize your matches to make every match different!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_4_2.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H5.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete in over 6 unique rooms of grandma\u2019s house, each packed with it's own challenges.  <br>Teleport with toilets, let the dog join the competition, play hot potato with grandma\u2019s old bombs, and freeze your opponents with ice cubes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_7.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H6.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Play as a mischievous kid who you can fully customize. Put on a lion outfit, dress like a princess or become goth  and bring your unique flair to the game. Show off your style as you destroy your competition!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/Footsy_Gif_2.gif?t=1737720890\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028560/extras/H7.png?t=1737720890\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Footsy is best enjoyed with controllers</strong>, and we support Xbox, PlayStation, Switch, and many more. Gather your friends, grab a controller, and get ready for wil